<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Lint on Abra's Blog</title><link>https://inshomepgup.github.io/blog-hugo-stack/categories/lint/</link><description>Recent content in Lint on Abra's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://inshomepgup.github.io/blog-hugo-stack/categories/lint/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>用simple-git-hooks + lint-staged来整理代码</title><link>https://inshomepgup.github.io/blog-hugo-stack/programming/frontend/lint/simplegithook/%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://inshomepgup.github.io/blog-hugo-stack/programming/frontend/lint/simplegithook/%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/142687600?s=48&amp;amp;v=4"
loading="lazy"
alt="Owner avatar"
> &lt;strong>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/lint-staged/lint-staged" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>lint-staged&lt;/a>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/33755274?s=48&amp;amp;v=4"
loading="lazy"
alt="Owner avatar"
> &lt;strong>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/toplenboren/simple-git-hooks" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>simple-git-hooks&lt;/a>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>两个项目&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 安装两个包到项目&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pnpm add lint-staged simple-git-hooks
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>package.json 添加如下配置。
这个配置就是设置在commit之前的hook执行内容。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;simple-git-hooks&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;pre-commit&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;npx lint-staged&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;lint-staged&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;*&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;eslint . --fix&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 执行如下命令初始化hooks&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">npx simple-git-hooks
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>得到信息：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">[INFO] Successfully set the pre-commit with command: npx lint-staged
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">[INFO] Successfully set all git hooks
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>后续的 提交的时候都会执行eslint . &amp;ndash;fix了&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>antfu-eslint-config</title><link>https://inshomepgup.github.io/blog-hugo-stack/programming/frontend/lint/eslint/antfu-eslint/</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://inshomepgup.github.io/blog-hugo-stack/programming/frontend/lint/eslint/antfu-eslint/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/11247099?s=48&amp;amp;v=4"
loading="lazy"
alt="Owner avatar"
> &lt;strong>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/antfu/eslint-config" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>eslint-config&lt;/a>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>antfu 大佬的eslint项目，非常好用。
平常前端最烦恼的一个问题是eslint和prettier都包含有format的功能，难以统一。
比如我碰到过用eslint format以后，prettier又爆红了，因为两个format规则有冲突。
这个项目的特性，很爽的一个点是:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Auto fix for formatting (aimed to be used standalone **without** Prettier)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>without prettier.
说实话我是非常的不喜欢prettier，配置困难不清晰，官方文档能给的支持非常有限。
各种强制换行还找不到对应的配置条目，很令人崩溃。&lt;/p>
&lt;h5 id="安装">安装
&lt;/h5>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pnpm i -D eslint @antfu/eslint-config
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h5 id="导入">导入
&lt;/h5>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-ts" data-lang="ts">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// eslint.config.mjs
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kr">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">antfu&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kr">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;@antfu/eslint-config&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">default&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">antfu&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h5 id="packagejson-去添加script">package.json 去添加script
&lt;/h5>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;scripts&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;lint&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;eslint .&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;lint:fix&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;eslint . --fix&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h5 id="ide-配置">ide 配置
&lt;/h5>&lt;p>eslint &amp;amp; auto fix on save&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="我的vue3的antfu-eslint配置">我的vue3的antfu-eslint配置
&lt;/h4>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">16
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">17
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">18
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">19
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">20
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">21
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">22
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">23
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">24
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">25
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">26
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">27
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">28
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">29
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">30
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">31
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">32
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">33
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">34
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-ts" data-lang="ts">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// eslint.config.mjs
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kr">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">antfu&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kr">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;@antfu/eslint-config&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">eslintObj&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">antfu&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">vue&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">true&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">typescript&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">true&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">ignores&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;src/vite-env.d.ts&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">rules&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;no-console&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;off&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;vue/html-indent&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;error&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;indent&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;error&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;style/indent&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;error&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;vue/block-order&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;error&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">order&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;template&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;script&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;style&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;vue/attribute-hyphenation&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;error&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;never&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;vue/max-attributes-per-line&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;error&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">singleline&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">max&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">multiline&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">max&lt;/span>: &lt;span class="kt">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;vue/html-self-closing&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;off&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">default&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">eslintObj&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>vue eslint 内置规则 所在目录&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">src/configs/vue.ts
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>用的不爽的rule可以用userConfig去覆盖。
内置规则去这里找源码查看就好了。src/config&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="一些尝试和理解">一些尝试和理解
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>进入源代码来理解一下这个配置应该怎么写。
github 的readme已经有很详细的配置写法了，不过我一开始用这个项目的时候也没太理解这个配置应该怎么写。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
